---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import StumpRemovalCalculator from '../../components/calculators/StumpRemovalCalculator';

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebApplication",
  "name": "Stump Removal Cost Calculator - Cincinnati",
  "description": "Calculate stump removal costs in Greater Cincinnati. Get instant estimates for stump grinding and full extraction.",
  "provider": { "@type": "HomeAndConstructionBusiness", "name": "Liteworks Co.", "telephone": "+1-513-927-9675", "areaServed": "Greater Cincinnati" }
};
---

<Layout
  title="Stump Removal Cost Calculator | Cincinnati Pricing | Liteworks Co."
  description="How much does stump removal cost in Cincinnati? Use our free calculator to get instant estimates for stump grinding and full root ball extraction. Get your exact quote today."
  schema={schema}
>
  <Header client:load />

  <main class="pt-20">
    <section class="bg-[#1a1a1a] py-16 md:py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Stump Removal Cost <span class="text-[#c4d931]">Calculator</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Get an instant estimate for stump grinding or extraction in Greater Cincinnati
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-[#f5f5f0]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <StumpRemovalCalculator client:load />
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SEO Content -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-6">How Much Does Stump Removal Cost in Cincinnati?</h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 space-y-4">
          <p>Stump removal costs in Greater Cincinnati typically range from <strong>$150 to $500 per stump</strong> for grinding and <strong>$300 to $1,000+</strong> for full root ball extraction. The main factors that affect pricing are stump diameter, wood species, accessibility, and the number of stumps being removed.</p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mt-8">Stump Grinding vs. Full Extraction</h3>
          <p><strong>Stump grinding</strong> is the most common and affordable method. A skid steer-mounted grinder chews the stump down 6–12 inches below grade, leaving the root system to decompose naturally underground. Grinding works for most situations — lawn restoration, garden beds, or simply eliminating a mowing obstacle.</p>
          <p><strong>Full extraction</strong> uses an excavator to pull the entire stump and root ball from the ground. This costs more and creates a larger hole, but removes everything completely. Choose extraction when you're building over the stump location (pouring concrete, setting a foundation) or dealing with a species that sends up aggressive root suckers.</p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mt-8">What Affects Stump Removal Pricing?</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Stump diameter</strong> — Larger stumps take longer and cost more. Most contractors price by the inch.</li>
            <li><strong>Wood species</strong> — Dense hardwoods like oak and hickory take longer to grind than soft maples and pines.</li>
            <li><strong>Number of stumps</strong> — Volume discounts are common. Getting 5+ stumps done at once is significantly cheaper per stump.</li>
            <li><strong>Access</strong> — Stumps in tight spaces behind fences or between buildings require more time and may need smaller equipment.</li>
            <li><strong>Root system</strong> — Surface roots that extend beyond the stump may need additional grinding.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mt-8">Cincinnati Stump Removal: What to Expect</h3>
          <p>Most residential stump grinding jobs in Cincinnati are completed in a single visit. A crew with a skid steer-mounted grinder can typically grind 5–10 average stumps in a half day. The wood chips from grinding are left in and around the hole — you can seed over them, spread them as mulch, or rake them out and bring in topsoil.</p>
          <p>Cincinnati's heavy clay soils can make full extraction more challenging, as root balls in clay tend to be denser and heavier. However, the clay also means roots don't spread as far as they would in sandier soils, keeping the extraction area more contained.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 bg-[#1a1a1a] rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-white mb-3">Ready for an Exact Quote?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">Our estimates are free and we'll visit your property to assess the stumps in person.</p>
          <a href="/get-a-quote" class="inline-block bg-[#c4d931] text-[#1a1a1a] px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-[Rajdhani] font-bold text-lg hover:bg-[#b5ca2d] transition">
            Get a Free Quote
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <a href="/services/residential/stump-removal" class="text-[#c4d931] hover:underline font-semibold">
            ← Learn more about our stump removal service
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
